1
00:01:24,800 --> 00:01:30,200
=Fights Break Sphere=

2
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:42,900
=Episode 3=

3
00:03:02,300 --> 00:03:06,400
Even without your teachings,
I would still be able to kill him!

4
00:03:32,200 --> 00:03:34,000
You're up?

5
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:35,400
Am I dead?

6
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:39,600
You're dead.
The Dragon Scorpio plunged you into a sifter.

7
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:42,300
It wouldn't be right if you didn't die.

8
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:48,700
In that case, won't I be like you,
having to stay here henceforth?

9
00:03:48,700 --> 00:03:51,400
What's wrong with staying here with me?
I can teach you Fight Qi.

10
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:53,800
I am already dead.
What's the point of learning Fight Qi?

11
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:56,300
I just want to teach you.
What's wrong with that?

12
00:04:03,600 --> 00:04:05,600
I don't feel like I died.

13
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:07,390
Lad, you hit a bonanza!

14
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:09,200
This whole pool is brim full
of Foundation Building Spiritual Solution!

15
00:04:09,200 --> 00:04:11,300
If the people outside were to see it,
their eyeballs would fall out.

16
00:04:11,300 --> 00:04:14,000
Only I, this old man,
would be so good to you.

17
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:15,510
It's full of Foundation Building Spiritual Solution in here?

18
00:04:15,510 --> 00:04:16,800
Yes.

19
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:25,600
You should rest for a while.

20
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,800
In a while, you should bow to me as your Master
during the disciple-master induction ceremony.

21
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:31,600
I will then begrudgingly give you some tips.

22
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:44,700
I won't bow to you as my master.

23
00:04:45,400 --> 00:04:47,800
Why not? I already agreed to teach you!

24
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:51,500
Is it so hard to bow to me? Do you know
how many people outside want me to be their master?

25
00:04:51,500 --> 00:04:54,700
I know. But once I bow to you
and acknowledge you as my Master,

26
00:04:54,700 --> 00:04:56,800
then whenever I see you,
I'll have to kowtow to you with my hands in front.

27
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:58,700
I won't do that kind of thing.

28
00:04:59,700 --> 00:05:02,000
Then, if we don't have a master-disciple relationship
and I'm teaching you,

29
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:04,400
what can the two of us be considered as?

30
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:08,700
A... partnership.

31
00:05:08,700 --> 00:05:10,200
- Partnership?
- Yes.

32
00:05:10,200 --> 00:05:13,000
Think about it. You pass on to me Fight Qi
and some martial arts skills

33
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:16,400
and I will help you to seek revenge.
You contribute the skills and I contribute the labor.

34
00:05:16,400 --> 00:05:19,800
We will definitely have an equal relationship.
What do you think?

35
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,800
Your father made the right choice
by placing you aside in the medicine shop.

36
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:24,200
You are good at doing business.

37
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:27,200
Of course! It's precisely so.
Do you think what I said is reasonable?

38
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:29,200
It is.

39
00:05:29,200 --> 00:05:32,800
But if you fail and ruin my reputation,

40
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:35,800
then I will be embarrassed.

41
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:39,300
So let's make this clear.

42
00:05:39,300 --> 00:05:42,200
On the matter of learning Fight Qi,
you must listen to me.

43
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:44,400
You can't talk back or rebel.

44
00:05:44,400 --> 00:05:46,000
When necessary, I will hit or scold you.

45
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:49,300
If you can't take it,
it's not too late to regret now.

46
00:05:49,300 --> 00:05:50,600
I will absolutely not regret it.

47
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:54,300
The Xiao Family is always honest
and never breaks a promise.

48
00:05:54,300 --> 00:05:57,800
All right, then let me ask you.
Where is the root of a person located?

49
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,700
Root...

50
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:02,400
Under one's foot?

51
00:06:02,400 --> 00:06:04,100
You are already wrong right from the start.

52
00:06:04,100 --> 00:06:06,100
An ordinary person's root is at the bottom.

53
00:06:06,100 --> 00:06:08,500
A practitioner's root is at the top,

54
00:06:08,500 --> 00:06:12,000
where the void is located.
You need to focus your thoughts in the void

55
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:15,200
and let the Foundation Building Spiritual Solution
fill up your whole body.

56
00:06:16,500 --> 00:06:18,200
How? How do I fill up?

57
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:21,200
Shut up and train properly.
You talk too much nonsense.

58
00:06:21,200 --> 00:06:22,800
Grand Old Master!

59
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:28,000
I will definitely, definitely master it.

60
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:51,700
The Fight Qi Continent has a total
of twenty-three types of Essence Flames.

61
00:06:51,700 --> 00:06:54,000
They are transformed from the Essence Qi of the Fight God

62
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:56,600
and spread out to twenty-three different places.

63
00:07:08,300 --> 00:07:12,900
My Essence Flame is called Bone Spirit Cold Flame,
which is just one type among them.

64
00:07:16,170 --> 00:07:18,810
What do you think? Do you want to learn?

65
00:07:22,200 --> 00:07:26,400
- If you want to learn, it still has to depend on
whether you have the talent for it. - How do we verify that?

66
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:30,100
Try to focus your Fight Qi skills
on the tip of your right finger.

67
00:07:41,700 --> 00:07:43,600
It's so hot!

68
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:50,300
You do have a bit of talent.

69
00:07:54,300 --> 00:07:56,400
I can create fire, too!

70
00:07:57,200 --> 00:07:59,800
Eight Extreme Collapse,
High Level Black Rank Fight Technique.

71
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:02,080
This Fight Technique is easy to start.

72
00:08:02,080 --> 00:08:06,000
But as your skills in Fight Qi increase,
it can almost be on par with the Earth Rank Fight Technique.

73
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:13,000
Eight Extreme Collapse.

74
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,900
It implies eight kinds of dark forces,

75
00:08:14,900 --> 00:08:16,900
and eight repetitive layers.

76
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:49,000
Eight Extreme Collapse!

77
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:52,700
If you use it well,
its power is unimaginable.

78
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:01,800
Xiao Yan, what are you doing?

79
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:05,100
You can't even watch over a bucket of water.
Hurry. Clean it up!

80
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:13,300
Hey, Xiao Yan. I heard that lately
you are secretly training in the Five Movement Fist.

81
00:09:13,300 --> 00:09:15,700
