82
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:20,100
There's no end to it for all of you, is that it?!
If you're that capable, go fight at the Soul Hall then!

83
00:09:20,100 --> 00:09:21,800
Hey, Xiao Yan.

84
00:09:21,800 --> 00:09:25,600
Aren't you a good-for-nothing since you're always
depending on girls to protect you?

85
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:27,800
Brother Xiao Yan, don't listen to his nonsense.

86
00:09:27,800 --> 00:09:31,200
It's fine. It was indeed me
who knocked over the pail.

87
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:34,400
There's no more Gather Spirit Herb Water.
I'll go back to the shop to make some again.

88
00:09:34,400 --> 00:09:36,800
Brother Xiao Yan, I'll go with you.

89
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:39,400
I will go with you, too.

90
00:09:44,400 --> 00:09:46,800
It's fine. Go on with your training.

91
00:10:25,300 --> 00:10:27,200
I'm just missing it by a little bit every time.

92
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:31,700
Don't be so greedy. This little bit is equivalent
to many years of hard work outside.

93
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:36,400
I heard that the Blood Spiritual Bug
has wonderful effects on training.

94
00:10:36,400 --> 00:10:38,300
Right?

95
00:10:38,300 --> 00:10:42,800
Yes, I know that, but I'm afraid you can't handle it.

96
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:44,300
Bring it.

97
00:11:01,900 --> 00:11:05,200
The Blood Spiritual Bug can immediately
open up one's vital channels.

98
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:08,100
The Foundation Building Spiritual Solution
can increase the stage of your Fight Qi Skills.

99
00:11:08,100 --> 00:11:11,200
And the Gathering Qi Powder
can help congeal your qi and blood.

100
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:14,800
Using all three together can help you
become a Fight Practitioner faster.

101
00:11:14,800 --> 00:11:17,200
Once you start using the Blood Spiritual Bug,

102
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:19,400
you can't stop the cultivation midway.

103
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:22,750
Once it travels through you, it's like
thousands of arrows shooting through your heart

104
00:11:22,750 --> 00:11:24,800
and much like an intense fire burning your body.

105
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:32,200
Once you've started,
you can't stop the cultivation midway,

106
00:11:32,200 --> 00:11:34,100
or else, the bugs will stay inside your body

107
00:11:34,100 --> 00:11:38,100
and eat up all your internal organs.
You'll then die from it.

108
00:11:38,100 --> 00:11:40,800
Restrain your mind and spirit.
Forget about everything and yourself.

109
