Stop moving around; otherwise,
the bugs will eat up all your internal organs.

115
00:11:57,000 --> 00:12:00,900
I'll go back to sleep now. Accompanying you
in your training every night is bad for my health.

116
00:12:00,900 --> 00:12:03,800
Grand Old Master! Grand Old Master!

117
00:12:07,300 --> 00:12:22,300
Restrain your mind and spirit.
Forget about everything and yourself.

118
00:13:22,300 --> 00:13:24,600
How long did I sleep?

119
00:13:30,160 --> 00:13:32,180
One exhalation, one inhalation.

120
00:13:42,100 --> 00:13:44,000
One exhalation, one inhalation?

121
00:13:44,800 --> 00:13:49,300
That's right. The time inside the Spatial Ring
is slower than outside.

122
00:13:49,300 --> 00:13:54,200
Think about it. I've been in deep slumber inside here
for a hundred years, but to you, it has only been seven years.

123
00:14:30,190 --> 00:14:31,970
Seven years.

124
00:14:33,300 --> 00:14:35,900
I've finally become a Fight Practitioner.

125
00:14:40,500 --> 00:14:43,400
Do you want to try it out?

126
00:14:57,600 --> 00:15:02,000
Good. Rascal, you are indeed gifted.

127
00:15:21,100 --> 00:15:23,100
Please come in.

128
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:27,400
Please enter.

129
00:15:43,090 --> 00:15:46,700
This year is the year for examination candidates
to compete in a grand competition.

130
00:15:46,700 --> 00:15:48,830
The three elders of Jia Nan Academy

131
00:15:48,830 --> 00:15:52,600
have come specially to our Xiao Clan's martial
arts skills training studio to visit everyone.

132
00:15:52,600 --> 00:15:54,500
This is our Xiao Clan's honor.

133
00:15:54,500 --> 00:15:57,000
Let me introduce them to all of you.

134
00:15:58,100 --> 00:16:02,900
Mister Han Feng, an elder of the Jia Nan Academy
and the current Pavilion Chief of Star Fall Pavilion.

135
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:11,200
Mister Ge Ye, an elder of the Jia Nan Academy.

136
00:16:14,310 --> 00:16:18,450
Mistress Ruo Lin, an instructor at the Jia Nan Academy.

137
00:16:21,300 --> 00:16:24,800
- Pleased to meet you, Three Masters.
- Pleased to meet you, Three Masters.

138
00:16:24,800 --> 00:16:27,800
Our Xiao Clan has always followed the ancient teachings.

139
00:16:27,800 --> 00:16:30,600
We only teach Fight Qi Skills and the Five Movement Fist.

140
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:35,500
Once they get admitted to Jia Nan Academy
and become a Fight Practitioner,

141
00:16:35,500 --> 00:16:38,400
that's the only time that we open
our Xiao Clan's Fight Technique Pavilion to them.

142
00:16:38,400 --> 00:16:42,800
They can learn Fight Techniques and Martial Arts Skills
based on their personal interests and habits.

143
00:16:42,800 --> 00:16:46,100
If they start learning Fight Techniques now,

144
00:16:46,100 --> 00:16:50,100
I fear that all will just end up as flowery fists
with fancy footwork. (showy but impractical skills)

145
00:16:50,100 --> 00:16:51,600
That's within reason.

146
00:16:51,600 --> 00:16:53,600
What Clan Leader Xiao said is very reasonable.

147
00:16:53,600 --> 00:16:56,700
In this journey of recruitment,
we've seen a lot of children.

148
00:16:56,700 --> 00:17:00,800
At their young age, their parents have already bought them
a bunch of Fight Techniques and Martial Arts Skills.

149
00:17:00,800 --> 00:17:04,700
In the end, not only did they not learn the basic skills
properly, they even developed a lot of bad habits.

150
00:17:04,700 --> 00:17:08,100
In the future, I fear that
it will be hard to teach them anymore.

151
00:17:08,100 --> 00:17:13,200
Xiao Clan Leader, may I ask...
where is your son?

152
00:17:13,200 --> 00:17:18,600
I heard that he is a reputable young talent in Wu Tan City.

153
00:17:20,400 --> 00:17:24,000
That son of mine only knows how to do flowery fists
with fancy footwork. No future at all.

154
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:27,400
For so many years, his Fight Qi has regressed a lot.

155
00:17:27,400 --> 00:17:29,000
I don't think he's suitable for this.

156
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:33,800
So I let him be an apprentice in the medicine shop.

157
00:17:33,800 --> 00:17:36,000
Xiao Yan!

158
00:17:40,020 --> 00:17:42,620
Greet the three elders.

159
00:17:43,350 --> 00:17:45,510
Pleased to meet the three elders.

160
00:17:47,480 --> 00:17:50,370
He indeed looks a lot like Senior Gu.

161
00:17:53,800 --> 00:17:56,700
Don't you know that your mother and I...?

162
00:17:56,700 --> 00:17:58,400
Elder Han.

163
00:18:00,900 --> 00:18:03,000
Matters of the past have already passed.

164
00:18:03,900 --> 00:18:08,100
I didn't mean anything by it. It's just
that when I see him, I think of an old friend.

165
00:18:19,600 --> 00:18:22,000
His muscles and bones are indeed a bit soft.

166
00:18:31,800 --> 00:18:34,900
Elders, let's go take a look at the front area.

167
00:18:34,900 --> 00:18:37,200
Sure. Please go ahead.

168
00:18:37,200 --> 00:18:38,800
Come, come.

169
00:18:56,100 --> 00:18:58,200
I fear that you won't be a shop attendant for long.

170
00:18:58,200 --> 00:18:59,400
What?

171
00:18:59,400 --> 00:19:02,400
You must think of a way
to get into the Jia Nan Academy.

172
00:19:02,400 --> 00:19:06,000
I indeed want to get into the Jia Nan Academy,
but why are you suddenly saying this?

173
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:09,100
Because I never thought that Han Feng
would also enter the Jia Nan Academy.

174
00:19:09,100 --> 00:19:12,940
Han Feng? My mother's junior?

175
00:19:14,180 --> 00:19:15,780
That year, during the final battle with Soul Hall,

176
00:19:15,800 --> 00:19:19,440
the person who really betrayed the team
and heavily injured me was him.

177
00:19:20,100 --> 00:19:24,200
So he caused my mother's death.
He's also the one who caused your death.

178
00:19:31,300 --> 00:19:33,200
Hurry! Run!

179
00:19:37,200 --> 00:19:39,150
Hurry! Run! Faster!

180
00:20:04,300 --> 00:20:07,700
If I hadn't let your mother transfer all the treasures
of Star Fall Pavilion in here first,

181
00:20:07,700 --> 00:20:09,800
and if those Fight Techniques had fallen into his hands,

182
00:20:09,800 --> 00:20:12,200
that would have really helped evil to victimize others.

183
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:14,600
He's now the Pavilion Chief of the Star Fall Pavilion.

184
00:20:14,600 --> 00:20:17,500
He will surely use all means to find the treasures and me.

185
00:20:17,500 --> 00:20:20,000
Shouldn't we stay further away from him then?

186
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:23,300
If I enter the Jia Nan Academy,
we will surely meet one way or another.

187
00:20:23,300 --> 00:20:25,900
Didn't you say often that you want to
seek revenge for me and your mother?

188
00:20:25,900 --> 00:20:28,900
If you hide once you see your enemy,
what revenge are you still seeking?

189
00:20:30,700 --> 00:20:33,700
I don't know what Han Feng's purpose is.

190
00:20:33,700 --> 00:20:36,800
Did he enter Jia Nan Academy
as ordered by the Soul Hall?

191
00:20:36,800 --> 00:20:39,300
And how does he plan
to go against the Five Great Clans?

192
00:20:40,700 --> 00:20:43,400
If you don't approach him,
how will we know?

193
00:20:43,400 --> 00:20:47,100
But I just ranked up.
How am I going to take the test?

194
00:20:47,100 --> 00:20:50,600
Just finish training your Eight Extreme Collapse
and it will be enough.

195
00:21:04,600 --> 00:21:07,700
Eight Extreme Collapse!

196
00:21:21,400 --> 00:21:23,000
Clan Leader.

197
00:21:37,800 --> 00:21:39,300
Bow!

198
00:21:45,800 --> 00:21:47,300
Begin.

199
00:21:55,100 --> 00:22:00,400
Fantastic!

200
00:22:01,900 --> 00:22:05,000
Xiao Xun'er, please come out.

201
00:22:06,200 --> 00:22:08,000
Be careful.

202
00:22:20,800 --> 00:22:22,500
Good! Good!

203
00:22:22,500 --> 00:22:24,000
Xiao Xun'er wins.

204
00:22:24,000 --> 00:22:26,500
Good! Good!

205
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:29,000
Very good, Xun'er.

206
00:22:35,190 --> 00:22:37,790
The next round is Xiao Clan's Xiao Ning

207
00:22:37,790 --> 00:22:40,150
against Jia Lie'ao!

208
00:22:40,150 --> 00:22:41,650
Good luck!

209
00:22:58,570 --> 00:23:00,230
- Are you all right?
- Come. Get up.

210
00:23:00,230 --> 00:23:02,460
Get up. Let's go.

211
00:23:04,310 --> 00:23:06,710
- Slowly...
- Quick. Have a seat here.

212
00:23:06,710 --> 00:23:07,940
- Sit him down.
- Help him down.

213
00:23:07,940 --> 00:23:12,130
Jia Lie'ao of Cloud Mist Sect has won.
If the Xiao Clan's disciples want to move to the next level,

214
00:23:12,130 --> 00:23:14,630
you still have one last chance in this round.

215
00:23:14,630 --> 00:23:17,320
Is there anyone from the Xiao family
who wants to accept the challenge to fight?

216
00:23:24,670 --> 00:23:28,130
Is there anyone from the Xiao family
who still wants to accept the challenge to fight?

217
00:23:28,130 --> 00:23:32,030
Father, let me have a go at it.

218
00:23:32,030 --> 00:23:34,670
Just deliver your water.
Why are you causing trouble here?

219
00:23:34,670 --> 00:23:36,490
Just let me try it.

220
00:23:36,490 --> 00:23:40,480
At this time, don't...
Did you hear me?

221
00:23:47,530 --> 00:23:49,540
I may not be able to win,

222
00:23:49,540 --> 00:23:51,850
