and will not easily give up.

225
00:23:59,090 --> 00:24:01,790
Is there anyone from the Xiao family
who still wants to accept the challenge to fight?

226
00:24:09,390 --> 00:24:12,130
I, Xiao Yan, a disciple from the Xiao family,
accepts the challenge to fight.

227
00:24:14,630 --> 00:24:16,670
Father, let me go up there instead.

228
00:24:16,670 --> 00:24:18,430
